OL,3,CCouncil to take full ownership of
OL,4,Crugby stadium in 'landmark' deal
OL,6,FA city council has officially struck a
OL,7,F"landmark" deal to buy the full
OL,8,Fownership of a sports stadium which
OL,9,Fhad an uncertain future.
OL,11,FSalford Council will take over the
OL,12,FSalford Community Stadium which is
OL,13,Fused by rugby league team Salford Red
OL,14,FDevils and rugby union club Sale
OL,15,FSharks.
OL,17,FIt already owned half of the 12,000-
OL,18,Fseat stadium, but will now go ahead
OL,19,Fwith purchasing the other half off the
OL,20,FManchester-based infrastructure
OL,21,Fcompany The Peel Group.
