OL,3,CCouncil to take full ownership of
OL,4,Crugby stadium in 'landmark' deal
OL,6,FThe deal includes the land around the
OL,7,Fstadium, which hosted the Rugby League
OL,8,FWorld Cup and the upcoming Women's
OL,9,FRugby World Cup in 2025.
OL,11,FSalford Council insists that the move
OL,12,Fwill help regenerate a significant
OL,13,Fpart of the city as well as offer more
OL,14,Fsocial, cultural, and employment
OL,15,Fopportunities for people in the area.
OL,17,FThe city Mayor Paul Dennett hailed the
OL,18,Fnews as a "landmark decision", adding
OL,19,Fthat it is the "beginning of a new
OL,20,Ffuture for the stadium and the clubs
OL,21,Fthat call it home".
