OL,3,CCouncil to take full ownership of
OL,4,Crugby stadium in 'landmark' deal
OL,6,FHe said: "It helps to secure their
OL,7,Ffuture, in particular Salford Red
OL,8,FDevils, but also the future of rugby
OL,9,Facross the city."
OL,11,FThe deal also includes ownership of
OL,12,Fadjacent community pitches, car park
OL,13,Fand associated development land plots.
OL,15,F"This is fantastic news for Salford
OL,16,Fand for rugby fans across Greater
OL,17,FManchester," Greater Manchester mayor
OL,18,FAndy Burnham added.
