OL,3,CCouncil to take full ownership of
OL,4,Crugby stadium in 'landmark' deal
OL,6,F"Mayor Dennett and Salford City
OL,7,FCouncil have taken an important step
OL,8,Fto protect our city-region's great
OL,9,Fsporting heritage and unlock new
OL,10,Fopportunities for growth and
OL,11,Fregeneration.
OL,13,F"The Salford Community Stadium is not
OL,14,Fjust a sports venue ` it's a community
OL,15,Fasset, and a symbol of our passion and
OL,16,Fambition for both codes of the game."
